{"tid":1707894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"千人添馬公園悼念周梓樂　高喊「香港人復仇」","createTime":"2019-11-11T11:58:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T12:26:53.000Z","uid":81228,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d5b2a0280638f5a5f7906562d29eb369c0b7143c","tid":1707894,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T11:58:30.000Z","msg":"香港科大學生周梓樂墜樓身亡，再度激起港民憤怒，發起一連串追思活動。9號5千多人在金鐘添馬公園舉行祈禱及追思會，警方發出不反對通知書，但要求參與人士必須遵守禁蒙面規範，現場還派出防暴警戒備，對在場人士一一搜查。<br />\n<br />\n追思活動晚間6點在添馬公園登場。現場湧入數千民眾在草地上席地而坐，高喊「香港人復仇」等口號，為墜樓死亡的周梓樂舉行追思會。民眾輪番上前獻花，並上台分享一路走來的心路歷程，台下也以熱烈掌聲，為勇敢的示威者加油打氣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsimg.ftv.com.tw/summernotefiles/News/5a6b8b88-77cc-429d-a8e2-b0f5b7a8a324.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsimg.ftv.com.tw%2Fsummernotefiles%2FNews%2F5a6b8b88-77cc-429d-a8e2-b0f5b7a8a324.jpg&h=fa52b6d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n反送中運動五個月以來，陸續發生多起疑似被自殺、爆眼、真槍射擊示威者的事件，而日前周梓樂墜樓，傷重不治，疑似被加工致死，不僅在示威者心理蒙上陰影，更引起港人對港警的不信任與憤怒。<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsimg.ftv.com.tw/summernotefiles/News/67563f1e-4e60-460d-bdd6-b001ef1bbe5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsimg.ftv.com.tw%2Fsummernotefiles%2FNews%2F67563f1e-4e60-460d-bdd6-b001ef1bbe5b.jpg&h=8031edae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而就在各界哀悼周梓樂過世同時，警方再出大動作，8號同天晚間以5月立法會肢體衝突為由，一口氣拘捕或預約拘捕7名泛民主議員。立法會民主派議員范國威表示，「我們有心理準備。我會服從 我會承擔罪證。」民主派議員梁耀忠則說，「今日即使這個特區政府和建制派，聯手打壓我們 我告訴大家，我們絕不畏懼，我們堅持這條路，要為社會帶回公平正義。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsimg.ftv.com.tw/summernotefiles/News/acd4da42-fb0b-4ee3-b431-aad473b3d6b0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsimg.ftv.com.tw%2Fsummernotefiles%2FNews%2Facd4da42-fb0b-4ee3-b431-aad473b3d6b0.jpg&h=4a886998&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其中朱凱廸、陳志全、區諾軒已於9號早上到警署完成報到。警方這番作為也被泛民派控訴，旨在火上加油、杯葛11 月 24 號區議會選舉。<br />\n<br />\n(民視新聞綜合報導）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ftvnews.com.tw/news/detail/2019B10W0007\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ftvnews.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F2019B10W0007&d=LL%2BPOpKvGkF1h1mPLRhV%2B2CvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=81df464c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ftvnews.com.tw/news/detail/2019B10W0007</a>"},{"pid":"a2b4a67d2dd866f8a24668efe5d7723d85d056df","tid":1707894,"uid":265168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:00:41.000Z","msg":"黃大仙1111戰略分析！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1707864\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1707864</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0c5178fb8bebc21b338272664bc081d6b6e1def9","tid":1707894,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:23:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bcb8e0d60b47e7d16f2815ef5c75ee4c04f1987d","tid":1707894,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:24:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24e9ba1283f0c09ac3fbd10f264ff8ff2cef1c9d","tid":1707894,"uid":34457,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:26:53.000Z","msg":"坐滿草皮 藍絲之前精密計算過 起碼三十幾萬人"}]}